</nav>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-12">
<!-- About -->
<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About the Product</h2>
<div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
<p class="mb-4">CloudScale Pro is the industry-leading infrastructure management suite designed for high-growth SaaS companies. Scale your operations with automated provisioning, real-time resource optimization, and enterprise-grade security protocols that keep your data safe and your costs predictable.</p>
<p>Whether you're managing a handful of containers or a global fleet of servers, our intuitive dashboard gives you complete visibility over your entire stack.</p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Gallery -->
<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Screenshots</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="aspect-video rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Screenshot of software dashboard showing analytics charts" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAc6b60KO3a-24WV7xV7WfG5cYHy2wljvymX621OJUjiOYlRDtcdFm5co-R3HCOqcSm3h4_spQwos8wuRPLG34hB5gyEcURJv4nIgeCOZoRDQW1pS4Bhq5L4kZgz5pmDeLByHyz_5CRSLcz5-wiHfVE-xdTROkaMrUzf7fT-asnbkNz6M-b_2R0xhi_zvVixlODkQqmgDylf218H0U5ZmUQ1dmtpeQi6Gq2kTPua_KLKFJAEuo-qOqfcK5l-sdgfFKAoqxNxzQxX_jy"/>
</div>
<div class="aspect-video rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Detailed view of user management settings" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAPdXHt930DHL1NqkL7SO5lyqOMWjGL4EmSJfrZzNIeXzYv0r6xNeEmB-LwrtgokyryH5SI7HuFrSYYAEUKB3X4EnP5ff1M2OVnqAE5I-9bVpUWKjyB4-N77lKw7RpGp5dfadRwgyRxE4ElIfTsC9KGuYicIvOEfBqBT_uY8L5EGdEpNGUnQ8SXBedcxO3D7Zk2YCoXlY1WpI_l3ahAlR3pj994Oe7oRK4SdVf0w3DnMzqSSR-G8eEwaGAwydOmEjeQ2qKU5ozP3i0t"/>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Features -->
<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Features</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50">
<div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">trending_up</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Scalability</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Automated resource allocation based on real-time traffic demands.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50">
<div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">shield</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Security</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">SOC2 Type II compliant with end-to-end data encryption.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50">
<div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">analytics</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Analytics</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Deep-dive metrics with custom reporting and alerts.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50">
<div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg h-fit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">api</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-bold mb-1">API Integration</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Full RESTful API support for custom workflows and automation.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Reviews -->
<section id="reviews">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Reviews</h2>
<a href="/support" class="text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:underline">Write a review</a>
</div>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
<div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-primary">JD</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm">Jordan D.</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">CTO, TechFlow Inc.</p>
</div>
<div class="ml-auto flex text-yellow-400">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
</div>
</div>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">"CloudScale Pro has completely transformed how we handle our backend infrastructure. The auto-scaling is seamless and the cost savings have been significant."</p>
</div>
<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
<div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-primary">SA</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-sm">Sarah A.</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">DevOps Lead</p>
</div>
<div class="ml-auto flex text-yellow-400">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined fill-1 text-[16px]">star</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">star</span>
</div>
</div>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">"Incredible tool for mid-sized teams. The API integration was very straightforward. Documentation is top-notch."</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
<!-- Sidebar -->
<aside class="space-y-6">
<!-- Pricing Card -->
<div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm sticky top-6">
<h3 id="changelog" class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Pricing Plans</h3>
<div class="space-y-3">
<div class="p-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary bg-primary/5 cursor-pointer">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
<span class="font-bold">Pro</span>
<span class="text-lg font-extrabold">$99<span class="text-xs font-normal">/mo</span></span>
</div>
